HEADWORD: Alectryomancy
<hw>A*lec"try*o*man`cy</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
cock + <ets>-mancy</ets>.]</ety> <def>Divination by means of a cock and
grains of corn placed on the letters of the alphabet, the letters being
put together in the order in which the grains were eaten.</def>
<rj><au>Amer. Cyc.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

